comment: Amazing food. Good portions. Delicious! Came here for a friend's reunion, the decorations are spectacular. Vintage!
The burgers are to die for!! Must try. Wings are especially my favourite. Also try the fajita, its wonderful! Definitely recommend!
Not the best but not the worst. Certainly one of the top 5 restaurants in magusa. Pleasant atmosphere, good music and good tasting food. Should try.
